trans-unit.source: Represents a single relationship between an object and a member.
<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> is used by a serializer to announce that one property is related to a property on another object.

<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> represents a single relationship between an object and a member that <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> uses in its interactions with a serializer.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> class.
The object that owns member.
The member which is to be related to owner.
owner or member is `null`.
Represents the empty member relationship.
This field is read-only.
A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> structure is empty if neither the owner nor the member is assigned.
Determines whether two <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> instances are equal.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> to compare with the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref>.

`true` if the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.
Returns the hash code for this instance.
A hash code for the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether this relationship is equal to the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty"></xref> relationship.
`true` if this relationship is equal to the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty"></xref> relationship; otherwise, `false`.
Gets the related member.
The member that is passed in to the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)"></xref>.
Tests whether two specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structures are equivalent.

The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%28System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship%2CSystem.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship%29?displayProperty=fullName>
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structure that is to the left of the equality operator.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structure that is to the right of the equality operator.
This operator returns `true` if the two <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structures are equal; otherwise, `false`.
Tests whether two specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structures are different.

The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Compare%28System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship%2CSystem.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship%29?displayProperty=fullName>
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structure that is to the left of the inequality operator.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structure that is to the right of the inequality operator.
This operator returns `true` if the two <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship"></xref> structures are different; otherwise, `false`.
Gets the owning object.
The owning object that is passed in to the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)"></xref>.
